                                        <p class="font_family_poppins mb_25">Drones equipped with AI can monitor crops, assess disaster damage, and even deliver medical supplies to remote areas. We should expect more pervasive automation in the coming years, leading to increased productivity and more job opportunities in emerging industries.</p>
